The folks over at @subu_tokyo_eu were kind enough to to send me a pair of their new winter sandals, right in time for the holidays. These might be the most comfortable sandals I’ve ever put on, like walking on a cloud. Perfect for lounging around the house, even better for the outdoors. Stoked to use these over the next few winter months. 

#wintersandals #subu @subu_tokyo_eu #ad

2022 has been one y’all. Fitting that the last day of the year resulted in Al and I scrambling to save my studio from the flooding in our garage today. All the gear is safe fortunately. While the floors are drying I went through the year in photos and these were some of my favorite moments. Happy New Year everybody, wishing y’all abundance and love in 2023!

Rearranged the studio a bit after the mini flood on NYE. Kinda missed having the pedalboards up on the dual keyboard stand so it’s a welcomed change. 

Currently working on a set for a live recorded performance in the coming weeks, excited to share more details soon!

Little afternoon mediation with help from the @hologram_electronics microcosm. The hold feature on this pedal is my favorite. Always leads to something unforeseen and unexpected. When I’m in my home studio, I’m always trying to find a good work flow. Being a musician, it’s all about being in the moment. When you find a sound that feels right, you really want to lean into it. With the August Wi-Fi Smart Lock I don’t have to miss a beat. I can quickly let someone in for a session from the August app on my Apple Watch. #sponsored

In the studio with threads from my good friends at @hiroshikato_official! Wild to know these are the last few sessions here in Oakland. Will be packing it all up soon and starting our new journey in the high desert!

Happy birthday to my golden ray of sunshine.
I’m so lucky to call you my wife, my partner, my best friend. Thank you for being you and always showing up with the biggest heart. I love you forever and I can’t wait to start this new chapter with you!
Yesterday shooting with @anthonykerrigan in @joshuatreenps. I can get used to these desert rides on the panhead for sure.
new places with familiar faces

I wanted to get Al something special to commemorate our time in the Bay Area and celebrate the start of our new chapter here in the high desert. I knew @portergulch was the way to go. They’re female run,  SF based and sustainably sourced and I found the perfect piece for Al and she loves it.

Last year I had the opportunity to join @waterstrider and record a special series of songs at @25thstreetrecording with @_tauwoo, @kvnmccann, @patrickaguirre_ , and @jeffkolhede. This clip is from, “Wasted Notes,” co-written by @_tauwoo and @waterstrider. Mixed, co-produced and drummed on by the talented @patrickaguirre_ 

The studio recording was released this week and is available on all the streaming platforms, be sure to check it out. Link in my stories! Cheers!

The early light here in the studio is something special. Making it a goal to be in here each morning and letting things unfurl as they may. 

Wrote a bit of this piece the other night when @brando__da came through, in another life we played in a band together. He left with blisters on his fingers but it’s a sweet baseline, thanks B.
